casebody.data:
No. 9,

Orig.

United States v. Louisiana et al. [For earlier proceeding herein, see, e. g., 452 U. S. 726.]

The Final Accounting of the United States, the corrected Final Accounting of the United States, and the Final Accounting of Louisiana are ordered filed. Objections to the Final Ac-countings are referred to the Special Master.

Justice Marshall took no part in the consideration or decision of this order.
